seed | a Common Sense CMS from The Media Collective

Status: 
Currently in early development. 

USAGE
1. Grab the app:
git clone git://github.com/desaperados/seed.git

2. Generate the database: (default is sqlite3)
rake db:migrate

3. Start your server:
script/server

4. Start using seed

CURRENT FEATURES:
- Site wide embedded editing. No separate admin section

- Page Creation and Management
  - Menu Hierarchy Ordering
  - Pagination Control

- Article Creation and Management  
  - Drag and drop Article Ordering

- Users Module
  - Restful Authentication
  - Roles
  - Account activation via email
  - Forgotten password handling

- Exception Notification
- Asset Packager

PLANNED FEATURES:
- Article Image Management
- Redcloth support
- Site wide search
- Pagination Control
- Themes